      • checkUpgrade

        StoreVersionCheck.Result checkUpgrade​(String desiredVersion,
                                      PageCursorTracer cursorTracer)
        Should only be called if storeVersion(PageCursorTracer) and configuredVersion() aren't equal. Checks whether or not the store version can be upgraded to the desired (i.e. from configured) version.
        Parameters:
        desiredVersion - store version to check whether or not the existing store is upgradable to.
        cursorTracer - underlying page cursor tracer.
        Returns:
        Result of the check.
